{"title_page": "Gander Terry", "text_new": "{{Infobox college coach\n| name = Gander Terry\n| image = \n| alt = \n| caption = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date|1907|9|24}}\n| birth_place =\n| death_date = {{Death date and age|1991|2|22|1907|9|24}}\n| death_place = [[Rapid City, South Dakota]]\n| alma_mater = \n| player_sport1 = Football\n| player_years2 = 1925\u20131928\n| player_team2 = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football|Western Kentucky]]\n| player_sport3 = Basketball\n| player_years4 = 1925\u20131929\n| player_team4 = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers men's basketball|Western Kentucky]]\n| player_positions = \n| coach_sport1 = Football\n| coach_years2 = 1938\u20131941\n| coach_team2 = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football|Western Kentucky]]\n| coach_years3 = 1946\n| coach_team3 = [[San Diego State Aztecs football|San Diego State]]\n| overall_record = 31\u201313\u20133\n| bowl_record = \n| tournament_record = \n| championships = \n| awards = \n| coaching_records = \n}}\n'''William Lester \"Gander\" Terry''' (September 24, 1907 \u2013 February 22, 1991) was an [[American football]] player and coach.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://digitalcommons.wku.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1034&context=stu_alum_papers|title=STU Alumni Papers|publisher=[[Western Kentucky University]]|access-date=December 6, 2018}}</ref> He served as the head football coach at [[Western Kentucky University]] from 1938 to 1941 and at [[San Diego State University]] in 1946, compiling a career [[college football]] coaching record of 31\u201313\u20133.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wkusports.com/sports/2017/6/8/ot-hall-of-fame-2-html.aspx|title=WKU Hall of Fame|publisher=[[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers]]|access-date=December 6, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Head coaching record==\n{{CFB Yearly Record Start | type = coach | team = | conf = | bowl = | poll = no }}\n{{CFB Yearly Record Subhead\n | name      = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football|Western Kentucky Hilltoppers]]\n | conf      = [[Southern Intercollegiate