o State]]\n | overall      = 6\u20134\n | conference   = 2\u20133\n | confstanding = 4th\n | bowlname     = \n | bowloutcome  = \n | bcsbowl      = \n | ranking      = no\n | ranking2     = no\n}}\n{{CFB Yearly Record Subtotal\n | name       = San Diego State\n | overall    = 6\u20134\n | confrecord = 2\u20133\n}}\n{{CFB Yearly Record End\n | overall  = 31\u201313\u20133\n | bowls    = no\n | poll     = no\n | polltype = \n | legend   = no\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Find a Grave|39934634}}\n\n{{Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football coach navbox}}\n{{San Diego State Aztecs football coach navbox}}\n{{San Diego State Aztecs athletic director navbox}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Terry, Gander}}\n[[Category:1907 births]]\n[[Category:1991 deaths]]\n[[Category:San Diego State Aztecs athletic directors]]\n[[Category:San Diego State Aztecs football coaches]]\n[[Category:Western Kentucky Hilltoppers basketball players]]\n[[Category:Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football coaches]]\n[[Category:Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football players]]\n[[Category:American men's basketball players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox college coach\n| name = Gander Terry\n| image = \n| alt = \n| caption = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date|1907|9|24}}\n| birth_place =\n| death_date = {{Death date and age|1991|2|22|1907|9|24}}\n| death_place = [[Rapid City, South Dakota]]\n| alma_mater = \n| player_sport1 = Football\n| player_years2 = 1925\u20131928\n| player_team2 = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football|Western Kentucky]]\n| player_sport3 = Basketball\n| player_years4 = 1925\u20131929\n| player_team4 = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers men's basketball|Western Kentucky]]\n| player_positions = \n| coach_sport1 = Football\n| coach_years2 = 1938\u20131941\n| coach_team2 = [[Western Kentucky Hilltoppers football|Western Kentucky]]\n| coach_years3 = 1946\n| coach_team3 = [[San Diego State Aztecs football|San Diego State]]\n| overall_record = 31\u201313\u20133\n| bowl_record = \n| tourna